OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMatheson says sons used    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FiPad to watch football     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Health Secretary Michael Matheson has  
OL,6, admitted an #11,000 data roaming charge
OL,7, on his iPad was caused by his sons     
OL,8, watching football.                     
OL,10,FThe bill was incurred during a family  
OL,11,Ftrip to Morocco last year.             
OL,13,FThe expense was initially picked up by 
OL,14,Fthe Scottish Parliament, which was told
OL,15,Fby Mr Matheson that the iPad was only  
OL,16,Fused for work.                         
OL,18,FHe has since paid the money back and   
OL,19,Fsaid he had referred himself to the    
OL,20,Fparliament for further investigation.  
